{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 271149, "create_time": 1656780542, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "诺兰的信条，星际穿越都不错吧", "timestamp": 1656780542}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 271197, "create_time": 1656783684, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "所有艺术形式在前中期都是容易突破的，到后期就会难以持续创新.. 不仅电影艺术，流行乐、小说、话剧的好作品都在枯竭.", "timestamp": 1656783684}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 271203, "create_time": 1656783984, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "而且你列举的片在艺术性上也并没有什么突破.", "timestamp": 1656783984}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 271209, "create_time": 1656784307, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "横向比较的话，华语作品还真称不上枯竭. 新世纪以来，华语导演可是拍出了不少现象级作品. ", "timestamp": 1656784307}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 271216, "create_time": 1656784618, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "《花样年华》《一一》《三峡好人》《刺客聂隐娘》这些亚洲电影的扛鼎之作都是21世纪的电影.", "timestamp": 1656784618}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 271244, "create_time": 1656786714, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "“业界要凉”永不过时", "timestamp": 1656786714}], "create_time": 1656779698, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1656786714, "likenum": 6, "n_attentions": 6, "n_comments": 6, "pid": 76808, "poll": null, "reply": 6, "text": "为什么近些年很少出现现象级的好电影了呢？尤其是像《泰坦尼克号》或者《盗梦空间》的这种兼顾商业性与艺术性的巨作。华语电影应该是因为审查制度所以很难达到上世纪90年代的水平，但放眼全世界来看为什么好作品在枯竭呢", "timestamp": 1656779698}}